    public class FeatureOrderEditor
extends FeatureModelEditorPage
    Additional editor page for the feature model editor. In this editor the order of the features can be changed.
    Author:
    Christian Becker, Jens Meinicke, Marcus Pinnecke (Feature Interface), Holger Fenske (replace swt.widgets.List with swt.widgets.Table), Edgar Schmidt (replace swt.widgets.List with swt.widgets.Table)
